<!doctype html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Seite nicht gefunden – virtauto</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
  <style>
    :root{--bg:#0f172a;--card:#111827;--fg:#e5e7eb;--muted:#9ca3af;--brand:#22c55e;}
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light){:root{--bg:#f8fafc;--card:#ffffff;--fg:#111827;--muted:#4b5563;--brand:#16a34a;}}
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{
      margin:0;display:grid;place-items:center;min-height:100dvh;
      font:16px/1.5 system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Ubuntu,Cantarell,Noto Sans,sans-serif;
      background:radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 20% 0%, #0b1220 0%, var(--bg) 40%), var(--bg);
      color:var(--fg);
    }
    .wrap{max-width:780px;width:100%;padding:32px}
    .card{
      background:color-mix(in oklab, var(--card) 92%, transparent);
      border:1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--fg) 14%, transparent);
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:28px 24px; box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    }
    h1{margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2px}
    p{margin:.25rem 0 .75rem;color:var(--muted)}
    .actions{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px}
    a.btn{appearance:none;border:1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--fg) 18%, transparent);
      padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--fg)}
    a.btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand), #38bdf8);border-color:transparent;color:#0b1220;font-weight:600}
    code{background:rgba(148,163,184,.15);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,.25);padding:.15rem .35rem;border-radius:6px}
    .hint{margin-top:14px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted)}
  </style>
  <script>
    setTimeout(function(){ window.location.href = "/"; }, 3000);
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>404 – Seite nicht gefunden</h1>
      <p>Die angeforderte Adresse existiert hier nicht. Keine Sorge – unser Live‑Status läuft weiter.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/">Zur Startseite (virtauto)</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/index.html">Status‑Dashboard öffnen</a>
      </div>
      <p class="hint">Automatische Weiterleitung in <code>3s</code> …</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
